title: Sprout Wholefood Cafe and Grocer
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Take-out, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Wholefood cafe next to the grocery market. Caters to multiple diets. Grows some veggies and herbs in an onsite gardens which are used in meals. Heaps of drinks like juices and smoothies plus a variety of treats in the cabinet by the cash register.
